description:
Created by Justice Action Media https://vimeo.com/justiceactionmedia and Maverick Media: https://maverickmedia.wordpress.com/ ORIGINAL: https://vimeo.com/14544003

Robert Parry, is the award winning investigative reporter who broke critical Iran-Contra stories as they unfolded. Here, he discusses events from that time and how they are impacting our ongoing situation in the Middle East.

Feb. 18, 2010

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
